# include <bits/stdc++.h>
using namespace std;
int main()
    {
    int t,i,j,k,n;
    cin>>t;
    while(t--)
              {
              cin>>n;
              bool flag=false;
              int hash[1005];
              memset(hash,0,sizeof(hash));
              for (i=0; i<n; i++)
                  {
                  cin>>j;
                  if(hash[j]) flag=true;
                  hash[j]++;           
                  }
              if(!flag) cout<<"YES\n";
              else cout<<"NO\n";
              }
    return 0;
    }
